Zen Programming Language,


What Zen is:
------------
Zen is a featherweight yet powerful language designed for both embedding
and stand-alone purposes. Zen is compact and requires little resource.
It is written in ANSI C, and compiles on many common platforms. It has many
useful features like dynamic typing and garbage collection. For a detailed
description of Zen, refer to the documents. Zen is
very young and still under rapid development, please keep a close eye on the
next release for more exciting new features!

Installing Zen:
---------------
Zen can be easily installed on different platforms. For the information of a
specific platform, please refer to INSTALL in the same directory.

Contacting the authors:
-----------------------
Zen's authors welcome any constructive suggestions, criticisms, and bug
reports. The authors can be reached at darklinkcompany[at]gmail[.]com